                <mxCell id="n5" value="Lines 171-183: Channel &lt;Select&gt; — OPTIONAL&#10;  Populated from channels array (useChannels). Shows channel_name, stores channel_id.&#10;  Restricted to pre-defined list only, no free text.&#10;  onValueChange={setChannelId}&#10;→ src/hooks/queries.ts : line 135 (useChannels → GET /api/channels)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="310" y="843" width="400" height="78" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

                <mxCell id="n6" value="Lines 186-249: Customer Combobox (Popover + Command) — OPTIONAL&#10;  Populated from customers array (useCustomers). Searchable, shows name.&#10;  User can select existing OR type a new name.&#10;  If typed name doesn't match any customer (isNewCustomer, lines 70-71),&#10;  an &quot;Add as new customer&quot; button appears (line 233-241).&#10;  Clicking it calls addCustomer.mutateAsync(trimmed) (line 76)&#10;    → POST /api/customers { name } → creates customer → closes popover&#10;    → src/hooks/mutations.ts : line 233 (useAddCustomer)&#10;  Value stored: customerName (string, not ID)&#10;📄 src/components/sales/AddSaleForm.tsx : lines 186-249" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="290" y="941" width="440" height="145" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

                <mxCell id="n7" value="Lines 251-266: For each part in parts[], renders a &lt;PartLineCard&gt;&#10;→ src/components/common/PartLineCard.tsx : lines 40-152&#10;&#10;Each PartLineCard contains:&#10;  Part Number: SearchablePartPicker (combobox, must select from items, no free text)&#10;    → src/components/common/SearchablePartPicker.tsx : lines 15-29&#10;    On select: handlePartSelect(index, itemId) runs (AddSaleForm line 111):&#10;      calls getAutoLocation(itemId) (line 95) — finds the location with&#10;      lowest stock for that item from inventoryOnHand, auto-sets location_id&#10;  Location: SearchableLocationPicker (combobox, must select from locations, no free text)&#10;    → src/components/common/SearchableLocationPicker.tsx : lines 15-29&#10;    Auto-populated by handlePartSelect, but user can override&#10;  Quantity: &lt;Input type=&quot;number&quot; min=&quot;1&quot;&gt; — required, integer ≥ 1&#10;  Unit Price: &lt;Input type=&quot;number&quot; step=&quot;0.01&quot; min=&quot;0&quot;&gt; — required, number ≥ 0&#10;  Currency: &lt;Select&gt; with hardcoded options: £, $, € (defaults to £)&#10;    → PartLineCard.tsx : lines 138-148&#10;📄 src/components/sales/AddSaleForm.tsx : lines 251-266" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="270" y="1106" width="480" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

